description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Advanced Whole Body Circuit ' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights and Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The The Disciplined Grind vibe means No excuses, no distractions, just execute. This is especially good for When you want pure focus and efficiency. The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Total body work off Hydrow and 1-minute intervals on-Hydrow. Explicit lyrics. 

Max rhythm: 26, Format: EMOM...
